ng across all sectors</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">. This could be </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">based on a ‘developme</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">nt plan‘ </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">for each of the TINA priorities</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> broken down into manageable steps</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">Many SMEs cannot contemplate taking on high risk projects but they can offer a</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> desk</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> in their company. I</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">nvestment in paid interns could mobilise a graduate workforce with a common mission – mentored via web based tutorials. This would help companies to </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">gather the information needed</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> and help them to identify where the opportunities might be. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Time