able</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">s sect</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">or</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> - </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">when </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">persistent </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">power cuts </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">hit </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">the western Cape lead</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">ing </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> to chaos in h</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">ospitals, traffic control systems </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> etc.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> and threatened the future of</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> its tourism industry</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> SA </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">, government finally acted !</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">Cardiff city is already having to manage energy use acros</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">s the city to minimis</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">e the likelihood of black outs....</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">At the moment </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">we have many approa</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">ches from international organisations</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">(mainly government)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">wanting to learn from our research in offshore wind</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> wave and tidal sectors</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">, and to build their own industries. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">UK consultancies have benefitted from the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">R&amp;D / consultancy </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">experience in UK and we currently have a narrow lead in wave and tidal internationally. It is imperative that we maximise our efforts to bring these sectors to</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-s